<blockquote>
  <p>NexT is a high quality elegant <a href="https://jekyllrb.com">Jekyll</a> theme ported from <a href="https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next">Hexo Next</a>. It is crafted from scratch, with love.</p>
